# Local LLM Configuration (Ollama)
# Ensure Ollama is running locally with phi model
# Run: ollama run phi
# Ollama API will be available at http://localhost:11434/api/generate

# NextAuth OAuth settings
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your_google_client_secret
# GITHUB_ID=your_github_client_id
# GITHUB_SECRET=your_github_client_secret
# NEXTAUTH_SECRET=your_nextauth_secret (e.g. openssl rand -base64 32)

